project_descr: Developing African Mutual Accountability Standards For Aid Effectiveness

outputs.output_descr:
The African Mutual Accountability (MA) programme aims at building effective aid and development cooperation on the African Continent. This will be translated into a mutual accountability assessment questionnaire with indicators and methodology to strengthen capacities for mutual accountability in Africa. The expected outcomes of the programme are as follows:
